ygData.subject: Man-O-War - Paladin only 2HB
ygData.msgSnippet: If you missed it, you should check out EQLizer to see the Man-O-War - a paladin only 2 handed blunt weapon (19 dmg, 41 delay with Chaotic Feedback effect).  It
ygData.messageBody:
If you missed it, you should check out EQLizer to see the Man-O-War - a paladin only 2 handed blunt weapon (19 dmg, 41 delay with Chaotic Feedback effect). It will make the dwarven hearts beat quickly, although carrying the effect Chaotic Feedback appears a bit odd. A hoax?

Does anyone know where this weapon can be found?

Llorfindal / Thorwin
